Title: Allen Brain Map Human M1 RNA-seq logcounts
Description: Matrix of log-normalized values from 127 aggregated cell type expression profiles derived from the trimmed means of 76533 single cell nuclei from the primary motor cortex of 2 human brain specimens generated by the Allen Brain Map

Title: Allen Brain Map Human M1 RNA-seq colData
Description: Per-cell type metadata containing labels of 127 aggregated cell type expression profiles derived from the trimmed means of 76533 single cell nuclei from the primary motor cortex of 2 human brain specimens generated by the Allen Brain Map
